text: Vicente Madrigal National High School is a public high school in Binangonan, Rizal, Philippines. The school is named in honor of the late Philippine Senator Vicente Madrigal. Established in 1992 as Vicente Madrigal Municipal High School, it was elevated to a National High School status on May 25, 1995. ==References== Category:High schools in the Philippines Category:Education in the Philippines
title: Vicente Madrigal National High School
